text: Bestyakhsky Rural Okrug is a rural okrug (administrative division) of Khangalassky District in the Sakha Republic, Russia. It contains just two settlements: Bestyakh (its administrative center) and Charang.Official website of the Sakha Republic. Registry of the Administrative-Territorial Divisions of the Sakha Republic.
